# C++ library - full project (code + testing + build + tooling + CI). A reusable static
# library with a public API under include/ and no binary of its own. Consumers use git
# submodule + add_subdirectory, so there is no install()/export()/find_package()
# packaging and no Docker release matrix; see cmake-lib and workflows-lib. Testing stops
# at unit + integration: with no binary to spawn there is no functional layer, which is
# why integration is not optional here. Use cpp-lib-cli if the project also ships a CLI.
